oracle.spatial.spark.vector

Class SparkRecordInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • oracle.spatial.spark.vector.SparkRecordInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class SparkRecordInfo
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Holds a subset of a single record's data, typically, the spatial information which is represented as an instance of oracle.spatial.geometry.JGeometry. Additional record information can be stored as SparkRecordInfo's fields using the add and get fields methods.
    Author:
    hsaucedo
